text: Þonne gif hwylc godcundes hades man gemettrumod wurð and hine eft gewyrpð, þonne he of þære mettrumnesse ariseð and ærost to cyrcean gæð þonne onlute he swiðe eadmodlice to ealre geferrædenne and hine ætforan Godes weofode astrecce.
Þonne scylon þa geferan singan his gebed and cweðe sum mæssepreost þas collectan.
